title: Rotation when in background
text: When you connect a second device to the same meeting without audio, it doesn’t allow you to rotate the screen and it’s very annoying because sometimes you can’t see since it’s too small if a computer screen is being mirrored in the meeting. Please add/fix this!

title: Super Handy!
text: I am getting to really like Teams.  At first it was much different than Zoom, so wasn’t sure I liked all the extra functions.  Now I’m happy to have the extra functions to increase my efficiency.  I would really like to see a blur option to soften facial features:) Ya .. I know Teams supposedly has a Madeline type Ap, but I haven’t yet figured that out.  Please just add a slider bar to the main camera display .. to make it easy.
